        "generateUrl": "https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts",
        "setup": "Create or choose a Google Cloud project, then enable the API from the [Google Play Developer API page](https://console.developers.google.com/apis/api/androidpublisher.googleapis.com/). In [Service Accounts](https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts), create a service account. In [Google Play Console Users & Permissions](https://play.google.com/console/users-and-permissions), invite that service account email and grant the needed Play Console permissions. Use the service account to obtain OAuth 2.0 access tokens for the `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/androidpublisher` scope as described in [Getting Started](https://developers.google.com/android-publisher/getting_started)."
