        "setup": "Create or choose a Google Cloud project, enable the API from the [Google Play Developer API page](https://console.developers.google.com/apis/api/androidpublisher.googleapis.com/), then configure branding on the [OAuth consent screen](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent). In [Credentials](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials), create an OAuth client ID. Authorize for scope `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/androidpublisher`, then obtain and refresh bearer tokens as described in [Getting Started](https://developers.google.com/android-publisher/getting_started) and [Authorization](https://developers.google.com/android-publisher/authorization)."
      }
